{"title":"一位老华侨","authors":["桑恒昌"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":11,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位老华侨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桑恒昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通往故土的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身躯扶着双脚走过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双脚扶着拐杖走过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手指扶着地图走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累得发抖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目光扶着天空走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分辨南北。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带伤带疼的脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都缩成病榻下面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那双不会再穿上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆口布鞋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心事如蚕，至死"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也咬住那根银丝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你奇迹般的等待着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等儿子从黄帝陵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取回一捧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炙手可热的黄土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有黄土作床，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便可以"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵睡千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横睡万里。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}